### List all topics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics

### Create root topic
POST http://localhost:3000/api/topics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "JavaScript Fundamentals",
  "content": "Introduction to JavaScript programming language"
}

### Update topic (creates version 2)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/topics/{TOPIC_ID}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Advanced JavaScript Fundamentals",
  "content": "Deep dive into JavaScript concepts and advanced features"
}

### Update topic again (creates version 3)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/topics/{TOPIC_ID}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Comprehensive guide to JavaScript programming with examples and best practices"
}

### Get current topic (always latest version)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/{TOPIC_ID}

### Get all versions of a topic
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/{TOPIC_ID}/versions

### Get specific version of a topic
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/{TOPIC_ID}/versions/1

### Get another specific version
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/{TOPIC_ID}/versions/2

### Test invalid version number
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/{TOPIC_ID}/versions/999

### Create child topic
POST http://localhost:3000/api/topics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Variables and Data Types",
  "content": "Understanding JavaScript variables and data types",
  "parentTopicId": "{PARENT_TOPIC_ID}"
}

### Delete topic (should also delete all versions)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/topics/{TOPIC_ID}

### Validation test - Missing fields
POST http://localhost:3000/api/topics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}